{"tid":476504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"U20對手主席：如果中方還對藏獨旗有意見，就得考慮是否繼續參賽","createTime":"2017-11-22T05:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T04:31:03.000Z","uid":5195,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"24c9f29696fe3181f06250b8af5325a3c822fd2e","tid":476504,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"北京時間11月18日，中國U20國家隊在旅德首戰中0-3不敵肖特緬恩斯，比賽當中&ldquo;藏獨&rdquo;分子在看台上展示其旗幟，中國隊一度離場抗議。而德國足協副主席稱，在體育場內自由表達一些觀點是被允許的，此言論也受到了中國外交部發言人的批駁。<br />\n<br />\n中國U20參加接下來的比賽時也會繼續遇到類似情況。他們將在週六對陣FSV法蘭克福，而一些球迷已經通知俱樂部，將掛出類似標識。FSV法蘭克福也拒絕對相關言論和行為進行任何管控。<br />\n<br />\nFSV法蘭克福俱樂部主席米高爾-戈納表示：&ldquo;我們不會放棄基本權利，不會進行一點點屈服，包括言論自由。只要言論表達發生在法律範圍內，俱樂部就不會干涉。如果中方有問題，他們需要決定，是否依然要參加在我們國家進行的友誼賽。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"8f5990e81ffbc4fa22598b6f811b38d4a9280d8f","tid":476504,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7754e37b479f235550f4bd1499959ebe15d3f9","tid":476504,"uid":2436,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac3661d41b40d7d10facd688616ef620feb38f9e","tid":476504,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae14987bc0e2c8fd14ca294107d62f97aa46f4c1","tid":476504,"uid":20522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"死去德國畀人當狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13f47222fe09ac63924966bfec0f169e93e79ae","tid":476504,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"骨氣<img src=\"/assets/face